    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为灵界的浪人，踏上救赎之路，以畅快的 hack-n-slash 方式斩破外界领域中酝酿的邪恶。阻止不祥的霸主前进的脚步，但务必谨慎前行，因为每一个角落都潜藏着狡猾的诡计者、巨大的猛兽，以及暴虐的国王，考验你的意志。斩倒强敌并掠夺强力装备，改变你下一场决斗的节奏！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >大型多人游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在开放的领域中与新朋友或老朋友合作。并肩作战，击杀那些被认为单人无法战胜的最强敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332210/extras/b320ad1b13cef885f713f789ac1d8157.poster.avif?t=1767903356\" width=220 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332210/extras/b320ad1b13cef885f713f789ac1d8157.webm?t=1767903356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332210/extras/b320ad1b13cef885f713f789ac1d8157.mp4?t=1767903356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >永久死亡</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验永久死亡的刺激感，每一步前进都需要付出代价；然而，并非一切都如此可怕。你过往生命的荣耀将构筑下一段旅程，建立起一个强大的浪人王朝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332210/extras/613172961225c8155485b17be789fa15.poster.avif?t=1767903356\" width=214 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332210/extras/613172961225c8155485b17be789fa15.webm?t=1767903356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332210/extras/613172961225c8155485b17be789fa15.mp4?t=1767903356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你的外观</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过你穿戴的装备展示你的成就！每一件武器和护甲都会改变浪人的外观，同时还有可收集的帽子和宠物伙伴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332210/extras/ba6a7ddaf45a12af83d82c4d9f85b6c0.poster.avif?t=1767903356\" width=218 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332210/extras/ba6a7ddaf45a12af83d82c4d9f85b6c0.webm?t=1767903356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332210/extras/ba6a7ddaf45a12af83d82c4d9f85b6c0.mp4?t=1767903356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你的玩法风格</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >混合你的职业、装备和祝福，打造狂野而有趣的组合。你可以成为从黑暗中出击的潜行刺客，横扫敌群的野蛮战士，或是在远处支援的精准弓箭手！</p>",
